\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />之前個d其他人"},{"pid":"51621bd6f7ab54db0fab5dc53cf85b9c238a85fc","tid":2443158,"uid":213142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T01:36:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2bf1a55ab04e40a14a4ad9ad818ea649e4ef80e","tid":2443158,"uid":261819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"51621bd6f7ab54db0fab5dc53cf85b9c238a85fc","tid":2443158,"uid":213142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T01:36:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T01:56:42.000Z","msg":"香港d 雀都幾貴<br />\n所以真係有價有市"},{"pid":"2bf7e5cd3d35ff0981664d92d83f3b6aaa2695dc","tid":2443158,"uid":261819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T04:19:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f19a5c01c8c51e16f542d1e3ec4fac5704c31ad1","tid":2443158,"uid":261819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T16:41:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90c65205016ccc66934afefedb582e44231770de","tid":2443158,"uid":152589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T16:44:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />